(e.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/56723/', '', 'Brivaracetam, Topiramate, Ezogabine, Cenobamate, Lamotrigine, Lacosamide, Levetiracetam, Tiagabine, Oxcarbazepine, Rufinamide, Perampanel, More', 'Antithymocyte immunoglobulin (rabbit), Anifrolumab, Ravulizumab, Diroximel fumarate, Mycophenolic acid, Abatacept, Inebilizumab, Belimumab, Sutimlimab, Risankizumab, Antilymphocyte immunoglobulin (horse), More', 1767369485);
